## Troubleshooting

### Error: "Graph API error: Unauthorized"

- Verify admin consent was granted for User.Read.All
- Check that the Aembit access policy is active
- Verify the federated identity credential subject matches

### Error: "Network error"

- Verify the Aembit Lambda Layer ARN is correct
- Check Lambda has outbound internet access
- Review Aembit Agent logs

### Error: "Trust validation failed"

- Verify AWS account ID in Aembit trust provider
- Check IAM role name matches exactly
- Ensure Lambda is using the correct execution role

